#- 1, The Player Involved§0
§0
§0Kovio. Kovio is a complete faggot who dedicates >her life to spreading degeneracy and keeping everyone around >her poor, as seen by the ABR oligarchy, which is now De Facto instead of De Jure. Kovio is known to be against freedom 
#- of speech.§0
§0
§0R509. I lived through the Chanadian holocaust. My people were oppressed under the trap administration. We were subjected to random pearlings, threats, and abuse by the government of Viridian. Ryan founded the famous 
#- Individualist Front (IDF). Ryan was a proud /int/IS citizen , who stood against opression from Viridian. He would spend a week in the end without reason before his capturer set him free, when he would go flee to the wilderness for 2 weeks.
#- NES2. NES2 is a friend of R509. NES and Ryan found out they had so much in common that NES merged his party, the CPP, into the IDF. NES and Ryan went through it all together.§0
§0
§0ChrisChrispie. Before becoming "Literally Judas", he was a fellow IDF member
#- who won seats in Intis. Chris has an obsession with economics, commerce and TRADE DEALS. He merged the Conservative Party into the IDF.§0
§0
§0Prioma. She had fell in love with NES in the most autistic manner possible. She became
#- crucial to the IDF as she was a high ranking political offical in Viridian, which helped her to pull off 'The Ruse' (you will read about this later).
