#- 3. Details of NES2's Trial/The Ruse§0
§0
§0NES2 was put to trial by Kovio. It was largely a witch trial, but NES2 was found innocent. NES2 was legally defended by Manabee, the best lawyer I've ever seen. Prioma, during the distraction of the trial dropchested 
#- the ABR's wealth to a secret location, where HGHG, just freed by Prioma, would take half of the loot before giving the other half to me. HGHG would later submit to Kovio, telling >her that I had the other half of the wealth. Kovio ransacked my little
#- settlement. I was forced to give the wealth back to Kovio and then left with a mess. This ransack lead to me heading north with NES2 and founding the short-lived country of Benistan.
#- 4. After the ruse I headed north, it was far away from Chanada. I have become and exile. Me and NES created Benistan on a desolate island in the north. We made recruitment threads and managed to get a few newfriends before it went downhill.
#- Benistan went donwhill when Kovio discovered we were harboring an alt of Prioma (oops). So, without real proof or reason beforehand, we were chased out of Benistan, our town ransacked. I went to Hjaltland, where I was quickly unwelcome. In an effort 
#- to get down to the swamp NES said we'd flee to, I took the rail to Iria during the wee hours. I was found by a bounty hunter , whose name shall remain anonymous. He would later become one of my greatest friends and allies. My pearl was held in the Bryn 
#- vault for a week or so, and apparently I ate up 4 stacks of their coal during my time in the end. It was  then that I would spend time up in the wilderness, away from civilization, a lone hermit. Later, I would strike a deal with Hantzu which provided me 
#- with the kind freedom with a probation period until Febuary 2nd, though in effect Han was away from me and in Titan much sooner, de facto ended my probation period early. I logged on during late January to discover I've been banned from Chanada (again) in
#- a purge of fellow revolutionaries, including ChrisChrispie. This lead me to Chanos, where I live today as I write this and continue to make and record history.
#- Transcribed by Drhorrorshow§0
